              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">from My Much Hon<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> Friend at Helvedille.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y01A389O-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-1" n="1">Hail to the Sage Who from his Native Store</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-2" n="2">Produc'd a Science Never known before</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-3" n="3">Science of Words Once Jargon of the Schools 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-4" n="4">The Plague of Wise Men, &amp; the boast of Fools</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-5" n="5">Made easy Now, &amp; Useful, in Your Rules.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-6" n="6">Where Wit and humour Equally Combine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-7" n="7">Our Mirth at Once to raise and to refine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-8" n="8">Till Now Not half the worth of Sounds We knew</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-9" n="9">Their Virtual Value Was Reserv'd for <note place="foot">路Dean Swift.</note> You;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-10" n="10">To Trace their Various Mazes &amp; Set forth</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-11" n="11">Their hidden force and Multiply their Worth:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-12" n="12">For if to Express One's Sense, Our Words We Chuse</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-13" n="13">A Double Meaning. is of Double Use.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-14" n="14">Hail Sacred Art! by What Misterious Name</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-15" n="15">Shall I adore thee Various, and the Same?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-16" n="16">The Muses Proteus, Skill'd with Grateful Change</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-17" n="17">Through all the pleasing forms of Wit to Range;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-18" n="18">In Quick Succession Yet retain thr么 all</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-19" n="19">Some faint Resemblance of the Original.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-20" n="20">Hail Fairest Offspring of prodigious birth</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-21" n="21">At Once the Parent &amp; the Child of Mirth!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-22" n="22">With Chloes Charms thy Airy form can Vie,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-23" n="23">And with thy Smiles, as Many Thousands dye:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-24" n="24">The pleasing pain thr么 all their Vitals thrills,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-25" n="25">With Subtle force, and <note place="foot">路an Extreme proper Epithet.</note> tickles as it Kills;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-26" n="26">Thee too like her the dying Swains persue</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-27" n="27">As Gay. as Careless. as Inconstant too,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-28" n="28">To Raise Yet More thy Merit &amp; thy fame 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-29" n="29">The Cyprian Goddess Glories in thy Name</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-30" n="30">Pleas'd to be thought the laughter loving Dame.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-31" n="31">Nor less thy Praise, Nor less thy Power to Wound</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y01A389O-line-32" n="32">Thou lovely fleeting Image of a Sound.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
